  "system": {
    "description": "Discipline: None\nSkill: Arm Strike\nType: Normal\nQi: 8\n\nYou clasp your foe’s head and suck out their Dragon Spirit, causing them to rise as a Hungry Ghost that temporarily obeys your commands. Make an Arm Strike roll against Parry. On a success you do 5d10 Open Damage plus 1 Extra Wound as the person’s Dragon Spirit is drawn violently from their body and absorbed into your own. This invigorates you, bestowing 4 Extra wounds to your next Melee Attack. If the target dies, then he or she rises up as a Hungry Ghost immediately and serves you loyally for 1d10 hours. If you got a Total Success on your initial attack roll and the target dies, then he or she rises up as a Hungry Ghost immediately and serves you for 1d10 days.",
